{{version030}}
{{flavour|Conjures two balls of burning swamp gas adjacent to the caster. The balls will rapidly seek the nearest monster and burn them. Wizards attempted to copy this with the spell 'Foxfire', but their version is much less powerful.}}

'''Marshlight''' is a monster-only spell that functions identically to [[Foxfire]], except it is stronger. It creates 2 foxfire entities, which seek enemies.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Marshlight was added in [[0.26]].

